ebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67fab3a603d6f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67fab3a602988.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67fab3a5f2609.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67fab3a5edfc3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67fab3a5c8477.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67fab3a6033bb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67fab3a53f6eb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67fab3a5d6222.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67fab3a603bbf.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67fab3a62b7ed.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6803c267944be.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;I know a lot of you have been waiting on this mod. It took longer than expected to finish this as a lot has happened in my life in the past few months. Anyway, the wait is finally over! Not really much to say other than that this mod aims to give the game more life. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Some screenshots have other mods installed such as the no blur background mod to make the screenshots more appealing. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Note: It seems as if most cutscenes are pre-rendered so the character's will have the default black dot eyes but the mod will work just fine during regular gameplay. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Addition: I edited the game's digital icon for anyone that is interested in having the art style match. You just have to install/update Sys-Tweak for it to work properly. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I hope you all enjoy this mod as much as I have. I put in A LOT of work into this. Enjoy!</description>
