      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67d3936e39b61.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67d393d944bd8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67d39539c8c71.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67d39587ee04c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;Full Info about the mod can be found at &lt;a href="https://www.nxoptimizer.com/games/breath-of-the-wild/" target="_blank"&gt;NX-Optimizer BOTW Page&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;UltraCam Features&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Features UltraCam Beyond's FreeCam.&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;UltraCam (Free Camera)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sequencer&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Control Zelda in FreeCam&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Pause&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Teleport Zelda to FreeCam&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Hide Game UI&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Change FOV&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Forces Depth of Field to 0&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Dynamic Framerate&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Forces triple buffer for switch.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fixes Menu speeds&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fixes Snowballs breaking when falling at higher FPS&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fixes other small physics issues.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Internal Resolution&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Up to 1296p&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Any Aspect Ratios Support&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Other Features&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Change FOV&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Depth Of Field Control&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Level of Detail Control (0 being the highest)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Zelda Hood Toggle&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h1&gt;Want to keep up with the project development? Join &lt;a href="https://discord.gg/the-way-of-the-wind-1111435904687550587" target="_blank"&gt;DISCORD&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;b class="SelectedElement"&gt;Want to Support Creation of Other UltraCam and NX Optimizer? Check out my &lt;a href="https://www.nxoptimizer.com/ko-fi"&gt;Ko-fi&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://www.nxoptimizer.com/patreon/"&gt;Patreon &lt;/a&gt;for Exclusive Features.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;PSA : I'm not very active in here. So joining discord is an easier way to find me.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;WHAT DOES THIS MOD DO?&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;The primary focus of this mod is to improve the game's Quality and Visuals as well as the framerate at which the game runs and how well it runs at higher FPS.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The mod also allows you to enter a Freecam mode. Which also allows for the creation of cinematic keyframes and the teleportation of Zelda.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h1&gt;I'M HAVING TROUBLE UNDERSTANDING HOW TO USE THIS&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Please if you are having trouble, use the &lt;a href="https://www.nxoptimizer.com/" target="_blank"&gt;NX Optimizer.&lt;/a&gt; It makes it a lot easier to setup.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;Please credit the mod if you use it for other content, preferably.</description>
